73
00:03:25,410 --> 00:03:26,620
She also has another characteristic.

74
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:27,890
Her route control

75
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,290
and race strategy are excellent.

76
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:31,080
She is always able to maintain first place.

77
00:03:31,610 --> 00:03:33,050
