78
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,600
I thought she is just strong.

79
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:36,640
So when I trained,

80
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:38,610
I added weight and more food crazily.

81
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,410
