I'll go by myself.

97
00:04:08,450 --> 00:04:09,320
You mustn't peek.

98
00:04:09,330 --> 00:04:10,290
We won't. Just go.

99
00:04:10,290 --> 00:04:11,330
We won't.

100
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:16,600
