105
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,630
- I lost five pounds.
- Quick.

106
00:04:49,650 --> 00:04:52,000
Impressive! You lost weight quite fast.

107
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:52,960
Of course.

108
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,800
You don't know

109
