177
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:00,220
Task?

178
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:01,180
What task?

179
00:09:02,340 --> 00:09:04,260
The competition goal he asked about.

180
00:09:05,740 --> 00:09:07,620
I don't know what my goal is.

181
00:09:07,780 --> 00:09:08,780
Goal...

182
00:09:10,780 --> 00:09:12,900
By the way, I have something to tell you.

183
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:16,260
In this competition, you will encounter

184
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:19,020
Yang Xiaofei, whom you've been studying.

185
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:20,460
She is coming too?

186
00:09:21,780 --> 00:09:24,260
So I think your goal for this competition

187
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:26,020
should be to confront her directly

188
00:09:26,140 --> 00:09:26,980
and give her some trouble.

189
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,140
I...

190
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:30,340
Can I do it?

191
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:33,860
You stay here for now.

192
00:09:34,220 --> 00:09:35,380
I'll go get the camera first.

193
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:36,740
After checking the data, I'll come to you.

194
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:38,580
All right.

195
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:52,860
Forget it, I won't think about it for now.

196
00:09:56,220 --> 00:09:58,380
Competition goal...

197
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:53,380
During this time, don't think about anything.

198
00:10:53,780 --> 00:10:55,900
Just imitate our old rival Yang Xiaofei.

199
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:57,390
After studying her thoroughly,

200
00:10:57,500 --> 00:11:00,140
