as a training partner.

201
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:42,380
Lin Ge.

202
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:45,020
Lin Ge.

203
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:49,380
Wei.

204
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:52,620
Lin Ge, I want to sleep now.

205
00:11:52,860 --> 00:11:55,140
But I dare not turn off the lights alone.

206
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:57,660
Ok, let's go back now.

207
00:11:58,260 --> 00:11:59,100
Let's go.

208
00:11:59,380 --> 00:12:01,500
Time to sleep. We're going now.

209
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:11,220
Hello, everyone.

210
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:12,140
Welcome to the site

211
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:14,260
