212
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:16,140
Today we will witness together

213
00:12:16,140 --> 00:12:17,340
men's and women's 1500m.

214
00:12:17,340 --> 00:12:18,900
Lin Ge, I'm a bit thirsty.

215
00:12:18,900 --> 00:12:20,020
I want to drink water.

216
00:12:20,140 --> 00:12:21,460
Ok, there is a water dispenser here.

217
00:12:21,460 --> 00:12:23,460
I'll see if I can find any disposable cups.

218
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:29,100
Here.

219
00:12:32,380 --> 00:12:33,460
It's hot.

220
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:34,580
Hot?

221
00:12:34,620 --> 00:12:36,020
Then I'll get you some cold water.

222
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:40,540
Are you ok?

223
00:12:41,260 --> 00:12:42,100
I'm fine.

224
00:12:49,380 --> 00:12:51,260
What do you mean? You also like Wei?

225
00:12:52,020 --> 00:12:52,860
No.

226
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:54,380
Why are you so attentive to Wei?

227
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:56,020
When am I attentive to her?

228
00:12:56,020 --> 00:12:57,260
In front of me.

229
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:58,140
Just now.

230
00:12:58,860 --> 00:13:00,860
I am just concerned about my teammate.

231
00:13:01,260 --> 00:13:02,450
Since you care so much,

232
00:13:03,020 --> 00:13:05,140
