233
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:06,260
will be entrusted to you.

234
00:13:08,340 --> 00:13:09,180
You're really thoughtful.

235
00:13:12,980 --> 00:13:13,860
Feeling much better.

236
00:13:14,260 --> 00:13:15,100
Ok.

237
00:13:33,740 --> 00:13:35,100
You also need fresh air?

238
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:39,860
I need a quiet atmosphere.

239
00:13:41,140 --> 00:13:42,860
Gao Kai talks too much,

240
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:45,380
