255
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:19,660
Don't you need to get prepared?

256
00:14:20,260 --> 00:14:21,740
A person's energy is limited.

257
00:14:21,980 --> 00:14:23,100
You're not Xiao Shanshan

258
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:24,860
who just needs to take care of Xie Lingwei

259
00:14:24,860 --> 00:14:25,860
like a nanny.

260
00:14:26,340 --> 00:14:27,180
She doesn't need grades.

261
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:31,740
Seeing you were busy with taking care of her

262
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:33,620
made me more annoyed.

263
00:14:43,100 --> 00:14:44,900
I have already handed this task

264
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:45,950
over to Seven Gold.

265
00:14:47,140 --> 00:14:48,020
Is this ok?

266
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:50,540
Yeah, Seven Gold.

267
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:52,220
How could I not have thought of that?

268
00:14:53,380 --> 00:14:55,260
Then you won't be annoyed, will you?

269
00:14:58,020 --> 00:14:59,500
Seven Gold likes Wei.

270
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:02,500
Doing trivial things with a girl he likes

271
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:03,740
