272
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:05,020
What about you?

273
00:15:05,460 --> 00:15:07,740
Who do you want to do such things with?

274
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:10,000
We will compete tomorrow.

275
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,400
I'm already nervous as hell.

276
00:15:11,420 --> 00:15:13,040
Yet you still talk about such trivial things.

277
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:14,460
Hurry back to your room.

278
00:15:14,860 --> 00:15:17,140
I need to calm down my emotions.

279
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:18,220
Otherwise, if I encounter

280
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:19,540
Yang Xiaofei tomorrow,

281
00:15:20,140 --> 00:15:23,460
