00:30:07,820 --> 00:30:09,900
What train ticket?

565
00:30:10,340 --> 00:30:11,580
What does it mean?

566
00:30:15,740 --> 00:30:17,340
From mindset to techniques,

567
00:30:18,020 --> 00:30:20,060
your analysis is very insightful.

568
00:30:20,420 --> 00:30:21,740
From this perspective,

569
00:30:21,820 --> 00:30:23,740
Nie Chi, you are really smart.

570
00:30:24,500 --> 00:30:25,780
But now

571
00:30:26,020 --> 00:30:28,100
I want to tell you something more important.

572
00:30:28,980 --> 00:30:31,740
The national team never nurtures idlers.

573
00:30:35,780 --> 00:30:38,020
Does it sound particularly harsh?

574
00:30:38,460 --> 00:30:41,520
You think I am too heartless, right?

575
00:30:42,580 --> 00:30:44,340
The national team never nurtures idlers,

576
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:45,700
not only for itself

577
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:47,260
but also for yourselves.

578
00:30:47,740 --> 00:30:48,580
Think about it.

579
00:30:48,580 --> 00:30:50,380
What are your peers doing now?

580
00:30:51,100 --> 00:30:52,700
Some are preparing for NCEE.

581
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:55,100
Some have already entered university.

582
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:58,260
I know your family is well off.

583
00:30:58,660 --> 00:31:00,460
But time is fair

584
00:31:00,460 --> 00:31:01,500
for everyone, right?

585
00:31:01,900 --> 00:31:03,500
If you don't want to compete,

586
00:31:03,500 --> 00:31:04,780
then it's better to go study.

587
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:07,170
That way, your family can help you.

588
00:31:08,020 --> 00:31:08,900
- Mr. Li...
- And...

589
00:31:10,100 --> 00:31:11,300
Do you know how fierce

590
00:31:11,340 --> 00:31:13,420
the competition is for each province

591
00:31:13,460 --> 00:31:14,900
to enter the national team every year?

592
00:31:15,740 --> 00:31:16,940
The leaders in your province

593
00:31:16,980 --> 00:31:18,420
and your coach have chosen you,

594
00:31:18,700 --> 00:31:20,260
holding great expectations for you.

595
00:31:20,500 --> 00:31:21,820
You need to learn to cherish.

596
00:31:22,740 --> 00:31:24,820
From the city team until now,

597
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:26,340
I have no doubt about your passion

598
00:31:26,540 --> 00:31:28,740
for this sport and your abilities.

599
00:31:29,300 --> 00:31:30,260
But in the national team,

600
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:33,900
having no results means being eliminated.

601
00:31:37,180 --> 00:31:38,660
Lin Ge. Lin Ge.

602
00:31:38,900 --> 00:31:41,060
Just now Nie Chi didn't even have time

603
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:43,500
to pack his luggage,

604
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:45,340
saying he would get a ticket from Mr. Li.

605
00:31:45,340 --> 00:31:46,260
What does it mean?

606
00:31:46,580 --> 00:31:47,500
How long has he been gone?

607
00:31:47,940 --> 00:31:49,740
It's been about ten minutes.

608
00:31:50,060 --> 00:31:51,340
I put the clothes in the washing machine

609
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:52,300
and then came over to find you.

610
00:31:52,340 --> 00:31:53,180
It has been so long.

611
00:31:53,190 --> 00:31:54,500
You still have time to do the laundry.

612
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:56,020
So stupid!

613
00:31:56,460 --> 00:31:57,340
Lin Ge, wait for me.

614
00:31:57,340 --> 00:31:58,180
Come back, come back.

615
00:31:58,260 --> 00:32:00,220
What ticket? What does it mean?

616
00:32:00,340 --> 00:32:01,780
Gao Kai mentioned it the other day.

617
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:03,980
Being given a ticket means being returned.

618
00:32:04,780 --> 00:32:05,660
Returned... Oh no.

619
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:08,060
Returned?

620
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:12,260
Mr. Li, you talk to me this much.

621
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:14,500
Does it mean I don't need to get a ticket?

622
00:32:15,660 --> 00:32:16,500
Ticket?

623
00:32:21,020 --> 00:32:22,260
Gao Kai said it, right?

624
00:32:24,740 --> 00:32:26,780
He is just messing around all day long.

625
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:30,740
Am I temporarily safe now?

626
00:32:33,500 --> 00:32:34,540
Nie Chi, let me tell you,

627
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:38,300
everyone in the national team, including me,

628
00:32:38,500 --> 00:32:40,180
is only temporarily safe.

629
00:32:43,740 --> 00:32:45,420
Is he really going to leave?

630
00:32:45,820 --> 00:32:47,020
It was not easy to make it step by step

631
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:49,100
from the sports school to the national team.

632
00:32:49,100 --> 00:32:50,100
You know,

633
00:32:50,100 --> 00:32:51,420
he is quite annoying most of the time

634
00:32:51,420 --> 00:32:52,740
and likes to nag and makes me angry.

635
00:32:53,740 --> 00:32:55,340
But thinking he is really going to leave,

636
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:57,100
I feel quite flustered.

637
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:03,340
What's wrong with you?

638
00:33:05,060 --> 00:33:09,500
Lin Ge, Shan isn't going to leave, is she?

639
00:33:10,020 --> 00:33:11,540
What is going on here?

640
00:33:12,340 --> 00:33:13,180
This...

641
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:15,900
Nie Chi, are you ok?

642
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:19,420
I'm fine. What are you...

643
00:33:20,340 --> 00:33:21,740
What could happen to him?

644
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:23,940
Is my office so dangerous?

645
00:33:31,020 --> 00:33:32,820
Lin Ge, I'm going back with Jinting.

646
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:35,740
I was freaked out.

647
00:33:36,020 --> 00:33:37,740
Fang Chao said you went to get the ticket.

648
00:33:38,190 --> 00:33:39,260
You made a false report.

649
00:33:39,460 --> 00:33:41,660
I didn't know what's going on either.

650
00:33:42,260 --> 00:33:44,180
Mr. Li just wanted to crack the whip.

651
00:33:44,580 --> 00:33:46,100
He wanted to criticize me a bit more.

652
00:33:46,580 --> 00:33:47,900
But it was too noisy outside.

653
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:48,980
He couldn't take it anymore.

654
00:33:49,340 --> 00:33:50,740
We thought you were going to leave.

655
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,820
Now Mr. Li gave you a chance.

656
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:01,260
Will you stay?

657
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:04,700
This is a mental hurdle.

658
00:34:04,820 --> 00:34:05,700
I am not as confident

659
00:34:05,700 --> 00:34:07,540
as when solving technical problems.

660
00:34:08,380 --> 00:34:09,500
What do you mean?

661
00:34:10,180 --> 00:34:11,580
Do you need help?

662
00:34:12,500 --> 00:34:13,900
As long as you can stay in the national team,

663
00:34:14,060 --> 00:34:16,020
we'll find a way to help you solve it.

664
00:34:20,420 --> 00:34:22,220
Just tell us what problems you have.

665
00:34:24,620 --> 00:34:25,460
Let's go.

666
00:34:36,580 --> 00:34:39,500
Isn't it just overtaking, bro?

667
00:34:39,540 --> 00:34:40,980
Is it that difficult?

668
00:34:41,300 --> 00:34:43,220
Isn't it just a matter of overtaking?

669
00:34:43,220 --> 00:34:44,420
What are you afraid of?

670
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:46,940
Lin Ge just wanted to give you a high five.

671
00:34:47,140 --> 00:34:48,500
You didn't even dare reach out your hand.

672
00:34:48,620 --> 00:34:50,020
You are not a true man.

673
00:34:50,580 --> 00:34:52,420
You have great talent. So what?

674
00:34:52,620 --> 00:34:54,620
Do you want to be returned because of this?

675
00:34:59,220 --> 00:35:00,100
Isn't it just overtaking?

676
00:35:00,460 --> 00:35:01,980
Go to the ice rink to practice.

677
00:35:01,980 --> 00:35:03,460
I'll practice with you. Come on.

678
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:04,620
Come on, hurry up.

679
00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:07,580
You can't be my sparring partner.

680
00:35:09,020 --> 00:35:11,220
Few people in the team are qualified.

681
00:35:25,980 --> 00:35:29,090
♪Tears in my heart♪

682
00:35:29,450 --> 00:35:32,730
♪I've moved on♪

683
00:35:32,730 --> 00:35:36,600
♪I'm sad and restless♪

684
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:39,680
♪But I forgive you♪

685
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:43,040
♪I shouldn't have been obsessed with you♪

686
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:46,470
♪Should I leave or stay♪

687
00:35:46,580 --> 00:35:50,430
♪I can give up my dignity♪

688
00:35:50,430 --> 00:35:52,500
♪That I care about♪

689
00:35:55,670 --> 00:35:59,070
♪The past and former days♪

690
00:35:59,070 --> 00:36:03,410
♪All have gone♪

691
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:06,300
♪Let it go with the flow♪

692
00:36:06,300 --> 00:36:10,220
♪Memories are close at hand♪

693
00:36:10,220 --> 00:36:14,480
♪Behind those smiles with tears♪

694
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:17,400
♪Is silence♪

695
00:36:18,100 --> 00:36:19,960
♪Wave my hand♪

696
00:36:19,960 --> 00:36:26,510
♪Perhaps after I grow up♪

697
00:36:31,160 --> 00:36:34,230
♪I keep tears in the heart♪

698
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:38,040
♪Unknowingly, I already regret it♪

699
00:36:38,040 --> 00:36:41,850
♪I'm sad and restless♪

700
